OL,3,CResidents' anguish as sheltered
OL,4,Chousing in Somerset set to close
OL,6,FResidents at Ivy House in Wellington
OL,7,Ftell ITV News' Ben McGrail of their
OL,8,Fanger after learning their home is set
OL,9,Fto close
OL,11,FResidents living in sheltered housing
OL,12,Fin Somerset say they are angry after
OL,13,Ftheir provider has told them their
OL,14,Fhome is set to close.
OL,16,FIvy House is one of two properties
OL,17,Fowned by Abbeyfield in Wellington and
OL,18,Fwas
OL,20,FThe Old Vicarage is the other home in
OL,21,Fthe town also now set to close.
