OL,3,CResidents' anguish as sheltered
OL,4,Chousing in Somerset set to close
OL,6,FResidents were told on Tuesday 23
OL,7,FApril in a meeting that efforts to
OL,8,Fsell it had broken down and there was
OL,9,F'no other option' but to close the
OL,10,Fhome.
OL,12,FThe operator said it was committed to
OL,13,Fhelping people find a suitable
OL,14,Falternative, but many people living
OL,15,Fthere said they will refuse to leave.
OL,17,FAnother resident, 86-year-old Colin
OL,18,FBrockington told ITV News: "I don't
OL,19,Fwant to have my death caused because
OL,20,Fmy uncertainty of where I'm living.
