OL,3,CResidents' anguish as sheltered
OL,4,Chousing in Somerset set to close
OL,6,F"They've been very cruel this company,
OL,7,Fto put us in this impossible position."
OL,9,FThe home's longest-serving resident,
OL,10,FQueenie Hutchings, who is 97, has
OL,11,Flived at Ivy House for 29 years.
OL,13,F"I can't think of living anywhere
OL,14,Felse. I'm not going to live anywhere
OL,15,Felse. I'm going to stay right here",
OL,16,Fshe said.
OL,18,F"I would like to end my days here",
OL,19,Fshe added.
