OL,6,FAnother criticised the operator,
OL,7,Fclaiming it was not 'thinking about
OL,8,Fpeople' and instead 'only thinking of
OL,9,Fmoney'.
OL,11,FAn Abbeyfield spokesperson said: "The
OL,12,Fdecision follows an extensive
OL,13,Fconsultation process, during which we
OL,14,Fhave listened carefully to
OL,15,Frepresentations made by residents,
OL,16,Frelatives and staff and spoken to a
OL,17,Fvariety of stakeholders about the
OL,18,Fdifferent options available to try and
OL,19,Fkeep the home open and serving its
OL,20,Fcommunity.
