OL,6,F"Significant investment is required to
OL,7,Fmeet the standards expected by
OL,8,Fprospective residents and regulators,
OL,9,Fnow and in the future and the costs to
OL,10,Fcarry out this work, even if spread
OL,11,Fover an extended period, are too great
OL,12,Ffor us to meet.
OL,14,F"The past few difficult years dealing
OL,15,Fwith the impact of the Covid pandemic,
OL,16,Fsector-wideJstaffing shortages, the
OL,17,Fhuge increase in energy prices, rising
OL,18,Finflation and rapidly increasing
OL,19,Foperating costs has impacted ALS's
OL,20,Fability to control costs and keep the
OL,21,Faccommodation affordable."
