OL,6,FThe operator added that in recent
OL,7,Fmonths it had been discussing options
OL,8,Fwith another provider regarding the
OL,9,Fpotential transfer of the home, but
OL,10,Fdue to the 'level of investment'
OL,11,Frequired, it was not a feasible
OL,12,Fsolution.
OL,14,F"We have been very proactive in our
OL,15,Fapproach, contacting local authority
OL,16,Fcommissioning teams and other housing
OL,17,Fproviders both locally and nationally.
OL,18,FAs well as other potentially
OL,19,Finterested parties.
