OL,6,F"Having explored all avenues we regret
OL,7,Fthat despite the home being very much
OL,8,Fpart of the community, we are not able
OL,9,Fto maintain it as a financial
OL,10,Fsustainable service that is fit for
OL,11,Fpurpose in the future.
OL,13,F"We are committed to working with you
OL,14,Fand the relevant authorities to find a
OL,15,Fsuitable home that meets your needs
OL,16,Fand were you will be happy."
